window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Isobel Carter is making headlines.</p> <p>Some of them good, some of them bad, and some of them … astounding.</p> <p>She started at the bottom and now she’s near the top with everything she never wanted, but the Ironside Show doesn’t care, because she’s just become one of the most interesting students at the academy, and everyone seems to have big plans for her.</p> <p>The only thing the Ironside fans can’t decide on is which Alpha she looks best with, because of course it all goes back to them.</p> <p>The precious, cherished, formidable Alphas of Ironside.</p> <p>The ten reasons why she’s in this mess to begin with.</p> <p>And what a beautiful, brutal mess it is.</p> <p>Beware the pretty liars, because this social media game just went from dangerous to deadly.</p>"; 
